<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #20c997;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
    .document-details {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .document-name {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #20c997;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>New Document Uploaded</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>
      <p>A new document has been uploaded to your account.</p>
      <div class="document-details">
        <div class="document-name">{{documentName}}</div>
        <p><strong>Document Type:</strong> {{documentType}}</p>
        <p><strong>Upload Date:</strong> {{uploadDate}}</p>
      </div>
      <p>
        <a href="{{documentUrl}}" class="button">View Document</a>
      </p>
      <p>If you have any questions about this document or need assistance, please contact our support team.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was sent to you because a new document was uploaded to your account.</p>
      <p>&copy; 2024 Tenant Experience. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 